 interpretation of this mechanism would be the\ncompression of trapped air between the grains by the surface tension of the\noil, or that of in pores by capillary forces, and the resulting decrease of the\nArchimedes force due volume reduction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 May 2008 17:09:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 May 2008 08:44:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 31 May 2008 13:18:40 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 13 Aug 2008 19:00:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-08-13"}
