lanned. It is shown that by observing the Moon\nfor $\\ge$ 1000 hrs using the ORT it will provide appreciably higher sensitivity\nthan past searches made elsewhere. Using the GMRT and ORT, it may be possible\nto reach sensitivity to test the Waxman-Bachall limit on UHE neutrino flux.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 May 2008 10:32:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-05-29"}
